{
  "stem": "20609.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he was in the bar, it was a nice bar and we had, you know, in those years you didn't have that many different drinks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But he had Cubas-- Cuba libras and old fashioned martinis and Manhattan, right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was the-- or Singapore sling, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I had a great job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So at the end of the season, this is those places close down like in April.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I meet a-- there was a dining room waiter that says to me, he says, I got a job in-- in-- in Cincinnati, Ohio, over on the other side of the river in Covington, he says, where the gaming is.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He says, I-- want to come with me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'm going to be the head waiter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'll make you a captain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I always admired captains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were getting money, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I didn't know if Cincinnati captains don't make any money, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So now-- [LAUGHS] so now he starts and we go to Cincinnati.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "This guy got a car and I drive with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You know, I didn't-- I-- I sold my car, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I think I gave it away or something or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was $200 I paid for it, I think I got $50 from somebody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so I drive this guy up to Cincinnati, I get into a hotel like a weekly hotel, and we go to work the next day, you know, like the place is just opening up.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he is there three days and he says, I got a better job, I'm leaving.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they made me the head waiter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I have-- I've been in this country less than a year, all of a sudden, I'm a head waiter.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
